SELECT followers.follower_id, user_profiles.username AS follower_username, followers.followee_id, user_profiles_1.username AS followee_username FROM followers JOIN user_profiles ON followers.follower_id = user_profiles.user_id JOIN user_profiles AS user_profiles_1 ON followers.followee_id = user_profiles_1.user_id ORDER BY follower_username ASC,followee_username ASC;
SELECT u.username, p.post_content, l.like_date FROM user_profiles u JOIN posts p ON u.user_id = p.user_id JOIN likes l ON p.post_id = l.post_id WHERE u.username = 'john_doe' ORDER BY l.like_date DESC
SELECT u.username, COUNT(p.post_id) AS total_posts FROM user_profiles u LEFT JOIN posts p ON u.user_id = p.user_id GROUP BY u.username HAVING total_posts > 5

SELECT u.username, COUNT(l.like_id) AS total_likes FROM user_profiles u LEFT JOIN likes l ON u.user_id = l.user_id GROUP BY u.username ORDER BY total_likes DESC
